    <p>Main contributers, people that are passionate about their industry and feel a sense of responsibility for shaping the future for the better.</p>
    <h6>Service owners and decision makers</h6>
    <p>Owners that find their services on this site can learn from feedback. Look at what others are doing well, and what others are doing wrong to be proactive.</p>
