    <h2>Road map</h2>
    <p><%= site_name %> is in the very early stages of development and our aim is to become fully community-driven. The site is under constant development with many new features to be rolled out as time.
    <ul>
      <li>Phase 1 - Getting Started - Available to everyone but with fixed moderators</li>
      <li>Phase 2 - Community-driven - Fixed moderated replaced by a system of reputation and merit</li>
